#  -*- Mode: Shell-script -*-
# ----------------------------------------------------------------------
# errors.test ---  test argument program attribute
#                    make sure that when it is not specified
#                    then option processing consumes all args.
#
# Time-stamp:        "2011-02-02 11:56:14 bkorb"
# Author:            Bruce Korb <bkorb@gnu.org>
